# Send via Gmail; deliver to Workspace inbox:
#   SMTP_USER=hvconciergeservices@gmail.com
#   SMTP_FROM=hvconciergeservices@gmail.com
#   SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
#   SMTP_PORT=587
#   NOTIFY_EMAIL=micah@hvconcierge.com
# SMTP_PASS = App Password for hvconciergeservices@gmail.com
# Inbox: "Jane Doe" <hvconciergeservices@gmail.com> → micah@, Reply-To = customer.
#
# App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#   (requires 2-Step Verification on the Google account)
#
# Test locally:
#   cd functions && SMTP_PASS='app-password-here' npm run test-smtp
